Ŵateŵeti ŵakwenera kupempha dankha ŵabwana ŵawo kuti ŵaŵaphalire dankha chakuchita pambere ŵandadumure chakuchita, ndipo ŵakwenera kulindilira kuti ŵapulikirenge ulongozgi wose uwo ŵapika.
